ESP8285 Based

For US (fan speed capacitors) - https://github.com/arendst/Sonoff-Tasmota/issues/5988#issuecomment-515720388

Photos - https://github.com/arendst/Sonoff-Tasmota/issues/5988#issuecomment-510177762

![](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/18605148/60994966-8c059300-a31f-11e9-82ff-783a13574e1d.jpg)

Disable buzzer with command `SetOption67 0`

The button is connected to GPIO0